I have fixed the Asset page for Component Submitted and implemented sorting. However, global sorting is not working for these fields.

Global sorting is currently not possible for MDLREND, BLDANM, BLDREND, and LDVMDL columns because their values come from MongoDB and are merged after the SQL query has already sorted and paginated the results. Since the SQL database does not have access to these Mongo values during sorting, it cannot sort the complete dataset based on them.
